<item>
            <title>[HIVE-24147] Table column names are not extracted correctly in Hive JDBC storage handler</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-24147</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It seems the `ResultSetMetaData` for the query used to retrieve the table columns names contains fully qualified names, instead of possibly supporting the &lt;tt&gt;getTableName&lt;/tt&gt; method. This ends up throwing the storage handler off and leading to exceptions, both in CBO path and non-CBO path.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
